edu.uga.cs.recdawgs.entity

Interface SportsVenue

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Persistable

    public interface SportsVenue
extends Persistable
    This class represents a sports venue for playing matches. A sports venue has a name, address, and is classified as an indoor venue or not. The name must be unique across all sports venues.
